long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension is to fill the input box on any form automatically. Its purpose is to fill the valid input to the form such as expired data, birthdate. If you found that the data it filled doesn't correct, please send a message to me. I'm more than happy to fix that for you.
